// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/l33yzN triangular grid on mountain wave, 2024 by jt
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ddcyRl textured terrain by triangle DDA
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mlfXD7 Triangle DDA via Voxel DDA Slice
// based on https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mtfXDM Branchless Voxel Raycasting Tex2
// clean-up of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/7dK3D3 Branchless Voxel Raycasting Tex
// building on voxel DDA of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/4dX3zl Branchless Voxel Raycasting by fb39ca4
// (with loop optimization by kzy), DDA based on http://lodev.org/cgtutor/raycasting.html

// A translucent triangular (prism) grid on a wavy mountain, implemented via ray-tracing a cube-grid dda.

// tags: 3d, raytracing, grid, terrain, raycasting, triangle, voxel, prism, heightmap, slice, dda, step, textured, triangular, polygonal

